title: The Wiggles: Wake up Jeff!
creator_credit: Dean Covell, Keiran Usher, Wiggles Touring Company and ABC-TV (Australia)
brief_description: Wake up Jeff! will have you jumping. Australia’s favourite children’s group “The Wiggles” are back singing and dancing in a brand new video. The Wiggles - Murray Cook, Jeff Fatt, Anthony Field and Greg Page, are joined by their friends Dorothy the Dinosaur, Henry the Octopus, Captain Feathersword and Wags his dog. Full of the songs and music that have made the Wiggles so well loved.
